        {
            "title": "簡訊：AI高算力PCB龍頭 勝宏科技招股集資175億港元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dJaiv5dBvKNhGECG5WSkLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/the_bamboo_works_186/bf53d397eee632dabaa58bb1e13f7a53\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
